      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Worm Bin\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = {{name|Fishing Skill Icon|link=Fishing|Level 4}}\n|ingredients = {{name|Hardwood|15}}{{name|Gold Bar|1}}{{name|Iron Bar|1}}{{name|Fiber|50}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Worm Bin''' is a [[Crafting|craftable item]] that can be used to create {{name|Bait|class=inline}} for [[fishing]]. The [[crafting]] recipe is unlocked at [[Fishing#Fishing Skill|Fishing level 4]]. One Worm Bin is the reward for the {{Bundle|Fish Farmers||y}}.\n\nThe Worm Bin automatically creates 4-5 pieces of bait every morning.\n\n==Cost==\nThe resources needed to construct a Worm Bin will sell for {{Price|845}}, without any professions. This means that it will take a Worm Bin about 42 days to pay for itself. If buying the materials (in Year 1), a single Worm Bin will instead cost {{Price|4675}}, and will take 267 days to pay for itself.\n\n==Crafting==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n|-\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredients\n!Recipe Source\n|-\n|[[File:Deluxe Worm Bin.png|center]]\n|[[Deluxe Worm Bin]]\n|{{Description|Deluxe Worm Bin}}\n|{{name|Worm Bin|1}}{{name|Moss|30}}\n|{{name|Fishing Skill Icon|link=Fishing|Level 8}}\n|}\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Can now be stacked in a player's [[inventory]] and in [[chest]]s.}}\n{{History|1.5|Fixed bug where processing time was affected by the time of day.}}\n{{History|1.6|Recipe is now learned at [[Fishing#Fishing Skill|Fishing]] Level 4 instead of Level 8. Now needs only 15 [[Hardwood]] to craft instead of 25. Now produces 4-5 bait every day instead of 2-5. Ingredient for [[Deluxe Worm Bin]] recipe.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n[[Category:Bugs fixed in 1.5]]\n\n[[de:Wurmeimer]]\n[[es:Vivero de cebo]]\n[[fr:Bac à compost]]\n[[it:Bidone dei vermi]]\n[[ja:ミミズ飼育器]]\n[[ko:지렁이 통]]\n[[hu:Gilisztásláda]]\n[[pt:Cesto de minhocas]]\n[[ru:Бак с червями]]\n[[tr:Solucan Kutusu]]\n[[zh:虫饵盒]]"
